data.description: Experience the allure of rural charm with this 4-acre hidden gem in San Antonio, Texas. This property offers a serene retreat with its secluded single-family home, featuring a welcoming front porch that sets the stage for a life of peace and privacy. Inside, the spacious living area, complete with a picturesque fireplace, awaits your personal touch and creative flair. Step outside to embrace the expansive land, ripe with possibilities for outdoor adventures and your landscaping vision. The property includes a large garage, perfect for vehicles, a workshop, or additional storage. The land itself, a blend of open spaces and lush mature trees, is perfect for gardening enthusiasts, outdoor recreation, or simply basking in the beauty of nature. This unique offering is an ideal investment for those seeking space, potential, and the chance to craft their dream sanctuary. Don't miss the opportunity to make this tranquil space your own. Book your visit now and start envisioning your future in this countryside haven.
